<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Nikki Webster rose to fame at 13, after she performed at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. </p>

<p>And on Monday, the 33-year-old Australian singer revealed fans can expect to be hearing more of her music soon.</p>

<p>Speaking to Nova's The Babble Nikki said: 'I have recorded music, I've recorded a whole album that I love and it's great fun, but I just haven't released it yet.'</p>

<p>'I've recorded a whole album!' On Monday, Nikki Webster (pictured) hinted at a music comeback 20 years after she rose to fame at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney </p>

<p>The Strawberry Kisses hitmaker described her new sound as 'fun'.</p>

<p>'It's fun, it's pop, it was [written] at a good time in my life... with some writers over in Nashville,' she explained.</p>

<p>'I went to write one song, and just ended up completing a whole album, so I do have music there it's just how to release it and when.'</p>

<p>Blast from the past! Nikki released her last single, Devilicious, in May 2009, but has not dropped an album since 2004's Let's Dance</p>

<p>Nikki released her last single, Devilicious, in May 2009, but has not dropped an album since 2004's Let's Dance. </p>

<p>Nikki became a child star after singing at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney, and went on to release hit single Strawberry Kisses later that year.</p>

<p>Last month, the singer shared adorable photos to Instagram of six-year-old daughter Skylah wearing her iconic pink frock.   </p>

<p>Her mini-me! Nikki (left) stunned fans by sharing photos of six-year-old daughter Skylah (right) in her iconic pink floral dress from the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney to Instagram last month</p>

<p>Skylah looked just like her famous mother did many years ago, as she posed in the signature outfit. </p>

<p>'20 years on from Sydney 2000 and I can no longer fit into the dress but someone else can!' Nikki captioned the sweet post.</p>

<p>Skylah wore her curly long blonde locks in pigtails with pink butterfly clips, adding to the likeness of Nikki's stellar look. </p>

<p>What a night! Nikki became a child star after singing at the Olympics, going on to release hit single Strawberry Kisses later that year (pictured in 2000) </p>
